    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 72-77.</p><p>Legendary Invocations</p><p>Also at 20th level, you have discovered Legendary Eldritch Invocations, great and terrible secrets from your Patron that increase your power substantially. You gain one Legendary Invocation of your choice.</p><p>You gain an additional Legendary Eldritch Invocation when you reach 22nd, 24th, and 25th level, as shown in the Warlock Table.</p><p>Cantrips</p><p>Invocations</p><p>Legendary Invocations Slots</p><p>Prepared</p><p>Spell Slot</p><p>Known</p><p>Known</p><p>Level</p><p>Spells</p></div>",
